ActCanadian Wheat Board Act
PrecisAuthority for THE CANADIAN WHEAT BOARD (a) to adjust its accounts, as of December 31, 2002, by transferring the balance of funds in the 1995-1996 pool accounts for wheat, amber durum wheat and designated barley, to a separate account, and (b) to make PAYMENTS to producers from that separate account.
